  "title": "Marketing Executive/ Manager (East) #HZO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Paya Lebar </strong></p><p>Job Scope: </p><ul><li>Support marketing campaigns planning and execution</li><li>Research industry-related topics and prepare well-drafted drafts or copy for social media posts, promotional emails and other marketing collaterals</li><li>Design or assist in the creation of written, video, and image content for marketing channels to advertise our company and products</li><li>Manage social media channels including Instagram, Facebook, Xiao Hong Shu, WeChat, Tik Tok and assist in replying to any customer inquiries</li><li>Ensure the collaterals created are consistent with the branding guidelines</li><li>Design customer success initiatives, or community events like fireside chats for customer engagement through Whatsapp channel</li><li>Plan lead generation events with key partners</li><li>Measure and report the results of marketing campaigns, social media ads and initiatives</li><li>Assists in any other ad-hoc data entry or administrative tasks as requested by the management</li><li>Design and lead team in offline marketing efforts (such as banners, pillar ads) and exhibitions</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min. diploma/ degree in marketing/ any relevant field </li><li>Min. 1-2 years relevant experience</li><li>Knows how to use Photoshop or Illustrator or photo editing software is a plus, but not compulsory</li><li>Knows basic video editing</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p><p></p>",
